Package metrics.aggregation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AggregationStrategy
    Interface for all aggregation strategies that will be implemented.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AverageDissimilarity
    Averages the similarity values and divides the average by the squared number of similarities.
    AverageValue
    Aggregation strategy that averages the similarity values to represent the overall similarity of the test cases compared.
    Euclidean
    Squares all the similarities and returns the square root of the sum of squares.
    Manhattan
    Sums the absolute value of all similarities.
    MaximumValue
    Aggregation strategy that chooses the highest similarity value to represent the overall similarity of the test cases compared.
    MedianValue
    Aggregation strategy that chooses the median similarity value to represent the overall similarity of the test cases compared.
    MinimumValue
    Aggregation strategy that chooses the lowest similarity value to represent the overall similarity of the test cases compared.
    ModeValue
    Aggregation strategy that chooses the most frequent similarity value to represent the overall similarity of the test cases compared.
    SquaredSummation
    Squares all the similarities and returns the summation.
    Summation
    Sums all signed similarities.
